title: Icelandic singer Sunna Margrét  performs "Chocolate" and more from her debut Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Sunna Margrét performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded October 3, 2024.

Songs:
Come With Me 00:43
Chocolate 06:50
Amma 11:28
Art Of History 15:28

Sunna Margrét - Vocals, Electric Bass
Sigurlaug Thorarensen - Electric Guitar, Backing Vocals
Hermigervill - Synth
Sólrún Mjöll Kjartansdóttir - Drums

Host: Kevin Cole

Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Leah Franks & Luke Knecht
